    "description": "We at ECIL South Asia Partners are looking for an experienced Full Stack Developer based out of Delhi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout ECIL South Asia Partners:\nECIL South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Flexible working hours\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ECIL South Asia Partners!",
